Imho WoG sucks.  I'm not there yet, but I've got 2 Jyll's and Supernova, and I can read spdat, and I know )<br>
<br>
Jylls (or chained multiple casts of Jylls) beat Winds on every front... dmg/mana, dmg in the smaller amount of time, chance of interrupt, etc....<br>
<br>
There are some rare circumstances where one could use WoG over Jyll's, just like there are rare circumstances to use Supernova.  If the mobs you are about to AE are not KoS to you, or at least won't aggro you because of green-ness.. and they're all standing near other to start with.... this would be a good opening spell, as the interruptibility and long casting time are somewhat negated.<br>
<br>
Even then.... kinda sucks to wait 6 seconds to follow up with Jyll's.  I guess the perfect scenario for it would be all of the above conditions + mobs that would be killed in one shot by this.... and I can't think of any practical situation that fits the bill.<br>
<br>
How could it be fixed?<br>
<br>
Current Stats on Jyll's Ice+Heat chained:<br>
Dmg: 1242<br>
Total Cast+Recover: 8.5<br>
Total Mana: 655<br>
<br>
Current Stats on WoG:<br>
Dmg: 1260<br>
Cast+Recover: 12.0<br>
Mana: 875<br>
<br>
Recommended Fixed WoG Stats:<br>
Dmg: 1260<br>
Mana: 630<br>
Cast: 5.0<br>
Recover: 2.5<br>
Recast: 12.0<br>
<br>
The &quot;new&quot; WoG would put out a mere 18 more dmg per target for 15 less mana per cast as 2 Jyll's chained, giving it a ratio of 2.0 exactly.  The only difference is that with the above timings it would accomplish this in a total time of 7.5 seconds instead of Jyll's 8.5 - 1 second faster.  And it would still have it's full 12 second recast.  That's not an unreasonable L60 upgrade I don't think.<br>
<br>
So the fix is... drop cast time to 5.0, drop recover time to 2.5, and drop mana to 630.  It is then a true minor uprgade to Jyll's that one would actually chose to open with in an AE group before using the Jyll's spells during the 12 second recast.  It is not overpowering. <p><BR>Cabot Coriolis of Tholuxe Paells<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urasenfeuer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rasenfeuer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:53:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Situational imo. <br>
